{"Id":865724,"Title":"浣溪沙三首·为筱婧题拙辑《近三百年名家词选》","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"龙榆生","Context":"饮水凭谁诉断肠。前身道是李重光。荷衣换却旧时妆。碧海青天风浩浩，蕙心兰质思茫茫。不思量处待思量。无益争能遣有涯。舌根徐吐妙莲花。几人肝肺共杈枒。看把须弥藏芥子，更教羲驭驻年华。鸥波映出脸边霞。黍谷温回合斗妍。苍生有分共春眠。木棉花发自参天。露染胭脂笼淡日，海浮楼阁感华颠。西江兀傲寄婵娟。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浣溪沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"8078ff8ee1518c6508ad8d31fbd80bfc","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5051878,"Sentence":"几人肝肺共杈枒。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī rén gān fèi gōng chā yá ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051871,"Sentence":"饮水凭谁诉断肠。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yin shui pǐng shéi sù duàn cháng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051872,"Sentence":"前身道是李重光。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qián shēn dāo shì li chóng guāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051873,"Sentence":"荷衣换却旧时妆。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hé yī huàn què jìu shǐ zhuāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051874,"Sentence":"碧海青天风浩浩，蕙心兰质思茫茫。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bì hǎi qīng tiān fēng hào hào ，huì xīn lán zhì sāi māng māng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051875,"Sentence":"不思量处待思量。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú sāi liáng chǔ dāi sāi liáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051876,"Sentence":"无益争能遣有涯。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mó yì zhēng néng qiǎn yǒu yá ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051877,"Sentence":"舌根徐吐妙莲花。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shé gēn xú tǔ miào lián huā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5051879,"Sentence":"看把须弥藏芥子，更教羲驭驻年华。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"kān bǎ xū mǐ cáng gài zi ，gēng jiāo xī yù zhù nián huā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":nu